{"tid":1494221,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「小學雞」專訪：沒想過會大四喜 艾馬利難取代雲加","createTime":"2019-08-21T14:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T07:57:16.000Z","uid":165817,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2042a61e6cec42604366dda2162267a2da103c7b","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zj5Vszs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZj5Vszs.jpg&h=d283ae76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　十年前，阿仙奴作客四比四賽和了當時力追榜首曼聯的利物浦。在那場比賽中，最令人難忘的無疑是兵工廠「沙皇」艾沙雲的大四喜。<br />\n<br />\n　　艾沙雲當時從辛尼特加盟阿仙奴僅三個月，但日前接受天空體育專訪時，艾沙雲表示，那對他來說只是一場普通的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n　　「對我來說，那只是一場普通的比賽，沒有什麼特別，在賽前我沒有任何特別的感受。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當我踏上球場熱身時，我在想『我們今天不會輸』，這是我賽前唯一有預感的事情。當然，我沒有想像自己會射入四球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當人們遇到我時，他們常常會向我提起這場比賽。我很慶幸自己參與了那場比賽，我也樂在其中。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「如果你只看數據的話，這確實是我職業生涯中最佳的比賽。但環顧整場比賽來說，我有其他踢得更好的賽事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcLa0Wi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcLa0Wi.jpg&h=9e63ef52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　那場史詩級的比賽已經過去十年，利物浦本週將在晏菲路迎戰阿仙奴。阿仙奴開季後取得兩連勝，這是他們十年來的首次，不過艾沙雲認為，艾馬利仍有許多工作要做。<br />\n<br />\n　　「雲加執教這支球隊超過二十年，要找到他的替代者是非常困難的，所以我覺得艾馬利現在的處境並不太理想，但是他第一年帶隊的成績確實不錯。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他正在打造一支球隊，這需要時間，我希望他能成功。保住聯賽前四是阿仙奴今季比較現實的目標，畢竟曼城和利物浦實在太過強大，他們是冠軍的爭奪者。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRXD9NM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRXD9NM.jpg&h=08b5aecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　艾沙雲在二零一三年與阿仙奴約滿後，返回了母會辛尼特，輾轉後在去年宣佈掛靴。雖然只在酋長球場效力了三年，但三十八歲的「沙皇」表示，自己一直會是阿仙奴的支持者。<br />\n<br />\n　　「我當然是個阿仙奴球迷，為什麼不是？在我在英格蘭的歲月裏，我只曾為阿仙奴效力過。我仍然是一名阿仙奴球迷，這一點永遠不會改變。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VT4ONzr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVT4ONzr.jpg&h=1a5061f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2817a13c0ba0a5532274e3dfd9e1b2ec31f5a61","tid":1494221,"uid":283207,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e7522e7dbe66bc8eae6599f5250de71e1c57d4","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"f2817a13c0ba0a5532274e3dfd9e1b2ec31f5a61","tid":1494221,"uid":283207,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係第一個因為加盟阿狗而令到我好開心嘅球員<br />\n第二個係奧燒<br />\n<br />\n好記得當年搞咗成個一月<br />\n好多個48小時 一時接近一時又失敗<br />\n最後係傾唔掂數 點知大風雪搞到艾沙雲飛唔到返俄羅斯<br />\n跟住好似過埋deadline先簽到 真係開心咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣成日小息 lunch 放學 都會偷用課室個電腦上網睇下有咩最新消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0387dccbf83c5764dc0342d47941df5ebbc7541","tid":1494221,"uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"原來已經38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c25308215b2c04a8b01f95c7898fb72f47124ca","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a0387dccbf83c5764dc0342d47941df5ebbc7541","tid":1494221,"uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"原來已經38<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"佢真係好遲成名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我第一次聽佢呢個名 係07-08歐協盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住一季後去阿仙奴已經係27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw佢08年歐國盃對荷蘭嗰場 係我見過最精彩嘅個人單場表現之一<br />\n去到120分鐘仲撚狗咁撚荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b5ffb33cfa19d6fbbeaf012cd902fba1899108","tid":1494221,"uid":35580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3d7350e3c345925fbaf847d8571424865620af","tid":1494221,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"對疤個場正D"},{"pid":"efbac98e9174d8682487a4aaee235a075e7412bd","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1mxu9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1mxu9F.jpg&h=c3a819d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十年過後，小學雞都出嚟做野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49425733356377a017b539b7aa25dfe3e9ec57c","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"cb3d7350e3c345925fbaf847d8571424865620af","tid":1494221,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"對疤個場正D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaUZUCq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaUZUCq.gif&h=2e13b6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皇應該利嗰場正啲<br />\n但對阿迷嚟講 一定巴塞正啲<br />\n當年要贏哥狗隊巴塞簡直係天方夜譚"},{"pid":"71d779d7c5d3988c1aa521f072f9daf42640a210","tid":1494221,"uid":107611,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"efbac98e9174d8682487a4aaee235a075e7412bd","tid":1494221,"uid":165817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1mxu9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1mxu9F.jpg&h=c3a819d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十年過後，小學雞都出嚟做野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:13:37.000Z"